'''阿富汗:能源供应改进投资计划'''的目的是从其他中亚国家[[輸電系統|输送电力]]至[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]，<ref name="protest">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-36305567 "What's behind Afghan power project protests?"], ''BBC Monitoring'', 2016-05-16, accessed 2016-07-24</ref>并将阿富汗国内十个独立电网整合互连。<ref>[http://thediplomat.com/2016/05/tutap-energy-project-sparks-political-infighting-in-afghanistan/ "TUTAP Energy Project Sparks Political Infighting in Afghanistan"] {{Wayback|url=http://thediplomat.com/2016/05/tutap-energy-project-sparks-political-infighting-in-afghanistan/ |date=20160719120240 }}, ''The Diplomat'', 2016-05-10, accessed 2016-07-24</ref>项目非官方名称为'''''TUTAP'''''，代表途径的国家（[[土库曼斯坦|土库曼斯坦]] - [[乌兹别克斯坦|乌兹别克斯坦]] - [[塔吉克斯坦|塔吉克斯坦]] - 阿富汗 - [[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]）。亚洲开发银行于2015年12月15日批准了该项目。<ref>[http://www.adb.org/projects/47282-001/main#project-overview "Afghanistan: Energy Supply Improvement Investment Program (Formerly Multitranche Financing Facility II: Energy Development 2014-2023)"], ''[[亚洲开发银行|亚洲开发银行]]''，2016-07-24访问</ref>

项目改道[[萨朗山口|萨朗山口]]，而不是原计划的[[巴米扬省|巴米扬省]]，导致[[哈扎拉人|哈扎拉人]]认为侵害了他们的权益，为此举行抗议。<ref name="protest"/>2016年7月23日，此次抗议活动中[[2016年7月喀布尔爆炸袭击|遭受炸弹袭击]]，导致80人死亡，260人受伤。<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/23/hazara-minority-targeted-by-suicide-bombs-at-kabul-protest 'Isis claims responsibility for Kabul bomb attack on Hazara protesters'] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/23/hazara-minority-targeted-by-suicide-bombs-at-kabul-protest |date=20160723153420 }}, "The Guardian", 2016-7-24, accessed 2016-7-24</ref>

